comment: * Package private utility class for ExifInterface.

methods.name: public static int copy(InputStream in, OutputStream out) throws IOException
methods.comment:
* Copies all of the bytes from {@code in} to {@code out}. Neither stream is closed.
     * Returns the total number of bytes transferred.

methods.name: public static void copy(InputStream in, OutputStream out, int numBytes) throws IOException
methods.comment:
* Copies the given number of the bytes from {@code in} to {@code out}. Neither stream is
     * closed.

methods.name: public static long[] convertToLongArray(Object inputObj)
methods.comment:
* Convert given int[] to long[]. If long[] is given, just return it.
     * Return null for other types of input.

methods.name: public static String byteArrayToHexString(byte[] bytes)
methods.comment: * Convert given byte array to hex string.

methods.name: public static boolean startsWith(byte[] cur, byte[] val)
methods.comment: * Checks if the start of the first byte array is equal to the second byte array.

methods.name: public static void closeQuietly(Closeable closeable)
methods.comment: * Closes 'closeable', ignoring any checked exceptions. Does nothing if 'closeable' is null.

methods.name: public static void closeFileDescriptor(FileDescriptor fd)
methods.comment: * Closes a file descriptor that has been duplicated.
